refactor(parser): simplify PDF parsing by removing OCR and table processing

Remove OCR and table structure processing options from the PDF parser as they are no longer needed. This simplifies the parsing logic and reduces unnecessary computations. The OCR_THREADS environment variable was also removed since it's no longer used.

Prepare environment for building GCC 6 on centos-stream-10

Update scripts and documentation to facilitate building GCC 6 from source on centos-stream-10. This change sets up the necessary environment for compiling GCC 6 across different Linux distributions.
